02:12.523 --> 02:13.959
GARRET:
Well, it's not all that
complicated either.

02:14.003 --> 02:16.179
ROBERT:
[over the phone]
Your mother's complicated.

02:16.223 --> 02:18.094
You fill out my absentee
ballot?

02:18.138 --> 02:20.966
