DRIVER: Hey!
ROBERT: Garret?

02:25.449 --> 02:26.929
DRIVER:
Are you blind?

02:26.972 --> 02:29.627
ROBERT:
[over the phone]
Garret? You on your bike?

02:29.671 --> 02:31.629
Yeah, I was heading to
the dorm.

02:31.673 --> 02:35.067
ROBERT:
[over the phone]
Don't answer calls while you're
biking!

02:35.111 --> 02:36.243
Yo Pop I gotta call you
back.

02:36.286 --> 02:37.679
ROBERT:
[over the phone]
Jeez.

02:42.858 --> 02:45.165
GARRET:
Wow. What's going on?

02:47.254 --> 02:48.646
Oh my God.

02:48.690 --> 02:51.127
[cameras clicking]

02:51.171 --> 02:54.304
[heart beat]

