03:10.755 --> 03:12.017
ROSE:
Any other ideas?

03:12.061 --> 03:13.671
BRITNEY:
Uh, we could hold an awareness
event?

03:13.715 --> 03:15.717
MALIK:
News flash! You know...

03:15.760 --> 03:17.327
this study just came out and it
shows that...

03:17.371 --> 03:20.591
students are aware that black
people exist, so thanks Britney.

03:20.635 --> 03:22.811
Alright. Anyone else?

03:22.854 --> 03:25.727
Okay. Thank you guys so much for
coming.

03:25.770 --> 03:27.424
I will keep you guys posted on
my meeting with the dean.

03:27.468 --> 03:31.776
We're doing this guys!
It's exciting.

03:31.820 --> 03:34.692
TREY:
Rose! Y'all gotta come see
this.

03:34.736 --> 03:40.829
[heavy music]

03:45.355 --> 03:47.444
[crowd murmurs]

03:47.488 --> 03:52.797
ROSE:
Oh my God.

03:52.841 --> 03:54.234
KEVIN:
Okay, so what are we gonna do?

03:54.277 --> 03:55.322
TREY:
Rosie!

03:55.365 --> 03:56.888
I have a meeting with dean
Marison.

03:56.932 --> 03:58.281
Marison's never done shit
for us.

03:58.325 --> 04:00.022
So why are you knocking on that
door again?

04:00.065 --> 04:02.242
What do you think we should do?
What do you think we should do?

04:02.285 --> 04:03.808
I wanna do something
different!

04:03.852 --> 04:05.157
Like what Trey?

04:05.201 --> 04:07.203
Like go to the Cracka house
and kick some ass!

04:07.247 --> 04:08.204
KEVIN [OS]:
What's a cracka house?

04:08.248 --> 04:09.727
MALIK [OS]:
Kappa house man.

04:09.771 --> 04:11.076
And who says they have anything
to do with this anyway?

04:11.120 --> 04:12.774
You don't think any of those
punks...

04:12.817 --> 04:13.427
have anything to do with this?

04:13.470 --> 04:14.341
Not necessarily.

04:14.384 --> 04:15.472
- Bullshit Rose!
- Come on Rose.

04:15.516 --> 04:16.298
Mind your business Kevin.

04:16.343 --> 04:17.779
TREY [OS]:
Oh my God.

04:17.822 --> 04:19.911
ROSE:
Trey. Do you even know what
this is about?

04:24.655 --> 04:31.880
KEVIN:
I got this okay? Lemme
just, lemme take care of it.

04:31.923 --> 04:33.577
God.

04:45.328 --> 04:48.200
NOLAN:
Dammit man will you just
make the call?

04:51.552 --> 04:54.250
You wanna see my cards?
Here. Here are my cards. See it?

04:54.294 --> 04:55.991
[door opens]

04:56.034 --> 04:57.688
TREY:
Afternoon gentlemen!

04:57.732 --> 05:02.389
Woah. Okay. Hello.
What's up?

05:02.432 --> 05:04.260
ALEXANDER:
Yo, we're not rushing
till next week...

05:04.304 --> 05:05.870
so you can come back then.

05:05.914 --> 05:08.395
Oh no, I'm not here to join
your little boy scouts club.

05:08.438 --> 05:12.834
Right. So why are you
here?

05:12.877 --> 05:14.705
I'm here because I was
walking to class today,

05:14.749 --> 05:20.842
