01:12:37.309 --> 01:12:38.310
MALIK [OS]:
It's gonna be alright!

01:12:38.354 --> 01:12:39.920
KEVIN [OS]:
You don't know that!

01:12:39.920 --> 01:12:40.878
TREY:
[on voicemail]
Hi. You've reached Tremayne
Torrance.

01:12:40.921 --> 01:12:42.270
Please leave me a message...

01:12:42.314 --> 01:12:43.837
