01:13:47.814 --> 01:13:48.989
Go get it.

01:13:49.033 --> 01:13:50.643
Holy shit Alexander.

01:13:50.687 --> 01:13:52.906
NOLAN: What? What?
GARRET: What the hell is that?

01:13:52.950 --> 01:13:54.386
ALEXANDER [OS]:
You just said it.

01:13:54.430 --> 01:13:56.301
