01:14:22.153 --> 01:14:24.895
SAM [OS]:
Okay. Alright.

01:14:26.374 --> 01:14:30.378
DETECTIVE HAVEN:
Who's idea was it to fake a
suicide?

01:14:30.422 --> 01:14:31.902
Alexander.

01:14:31.945 --> 01:14:34.252
