01:14:48.092 --> 01:14:49.659
[train in the distance]

01:15:17.513 --> 01:15:20.820
ALEXANDER:
Well?

01:15:28.567 --> 01:15:30.395
[ominous music]

01:15:47.151 --> 01:15:48.979
What happened after that?

01:15:49.022 --> 01:15:50.546
