whereabouts of...

01:16:12.524 --> 01:16:16.006
Alexander Kraus, Samuel
Boergadine, or Nolan Miller.

01:16:16.659 --> 01:16:17.834
No.

01:16:17.877 --> 01:16:18.748
DETECTIVE HAVEN [OS]:
Who else was there?

01:16:19.270 --> 01:16:20.140
GARRET [OS]:
I don't know. I--

01:16:20.184 --> 01:16:22.055
